SUPABASE_URL=https://dfhnmdjaulixiffpzzpp.supabase.co
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-service-role-key-here

# OpenAI — used for embeddings (text-embedding-3-small) and optional GPT-4o ranking
